                <h1>Does Peel and Stick Wallpaper Damage Walls?</h1>
                <p>Peel and stick wallpaper is generally considered a safe option for walls, as it can be easily removed without causing damage, especially if the wall surface is smooth and clean. However, if the wallpaper is left on for an extended period or applied to porous surfaces, it may leave adhesive residue or paint damage upon removal. Always check for compatibility.</p>
